{"word":"G3710 - ὀργίζω - orgízō - or-gid'-zo - Be angry","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀργίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>orgízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>or-gid'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be angry"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கோபித்துக்கொள், கோபமடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to provoke, arouse to anger"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3709 - ὀργή - orgḗ - or-gay'/3709\">G3709</a>; to <i>provoke</i> or <i>enrage</i>, that is, (passively) <i>become exasperated:</i> - be angry (wroth)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3709 - ὀργή - orgḗ - or-gay'/3709\">G3709</a>, <a href=\"#/G3710 - ὀργίζω - orgízō - or-gid'-zo/3710\">G3710</a>, <a href=\"#/G3711 - ὀργίλος - orgílos - org-ee'-los/3711\">G3711</a>, <a href=\"#/G3949 - παροργίζω - parorgízō - par-org-id'-zo/3949\">G3949</a>, <a href=\"#/G3950 - παροργισμός - parorgismós - par-org-is-mos'/3950\">G3950</a>"}]}